
   Goals Are Awesome
  =-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=

  We're tracking goals here.  For the good of all humans.

   Requirements for Developers:
  ------------------------------
    [sudo] gem install rspec-rails
    [sudo] gem install rubyist-aasm
    [sudo] gem install haml

   Warnings:
  ------------------------------
    Use the has_many_polymorphs plugin, rather than the gem 
      (gem rel v2.12 does not work with Rails 2.2.2).

   Setup:
  -----------------------------
    After cloning the project.  You can run the Rake setup
    task like so:
      $ rake gaa:setup

  ------------------------------
   Authors: 
    Dan Tripp <doktahworm@gmail.com>
    Kyle Oba <koba@mudphone.com>

    After install, create a user account (/signup) and login.
      Copy the YML from the home page (/home) to /spec/fixtures/users.yml